</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The row of children chant:{"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/e/e6/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/e/e6/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg/aid77669-v4-728px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet2-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
"What's the time Mr. Wolf?" Mr. Wolf will turn around and answer a time (for example, 4 o'clock). {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c7/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/v4-460px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/c/c7/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet3.jpg/aid77669-v4-728px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The children advance the number of steps called out and then repeat the chant, waiting for a response and so on. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/9/9e/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet4.jpg/v4-460px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet4.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/9/9e/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet4.jpg/aid77669-v4-728px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Eventually they will be standing very close to Mr. Wolf. Mr. Wolf can, at any moment once the line of children is close, respond "Lunch Time" in a loud growl, instead of giving a real time. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/6/67/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet5-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet5-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/6/67/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet5-Version-2.jpg/aid77669-v4-728px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet5-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

This is the cue for lots of screaming (remind them not to scream) and running because now Mr. Wolf has to chase the rest of the children and tag one of them. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/8f/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet6-Version-2.jpg/v4-460px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet6-Version-2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/8/8f/Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet6-Version-2.jpg/aid77669-v4-728px-Play-What%27s-the-Time-Mr-Wolf-Step-3Bullet6-Version-2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":345,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"546","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
